author: COMSOL
description: This example shows how to perform a Low Cycle Fatigue (LCF) analysis using a linear elastic model, even though the stresses at the hole are well above the yield limit. The plasticity at the hole is treated by an approximate method based on the stress and strain field at small notches.
label: cylinder_with_hole_elastic.mph
